Waytico favicon — "Three bars" (T-04)
========================================

Brand color : #C4622D (terracotta)
Background  : transparent (PNG/SVG); apple-touch-icon uses #F5F1EA paper

Files
-----
  favicon.svg               Master vector. Serve as primary favicon.
  favicon-paper-bg.svg      Same mark on paper-color tile (for light backgrounds where transparency reads wrong).
  favicon-16.png            Browser tab (small).
  favicon-32.png            Browser tab (retina) and bookmarks.
  favicon-48.png            Windows site icon.
  favicon-64.png            Generic.
  favicon-96.png            Android Chrome legacy.
  favicon-128.png           Generic.
  favicon-180.png           Reserve.
  favicon-192.png           Android Chrome / PWA.
  favicon-256.png           Generic.
  favicon-512.png           PWA splash / large.
  apple-touch-icon.png      iOS home-screen icon (180x180, non-transparent).
  site.webmanifest          PWA manifest.
  head-snippet.html         Drop into <head>.

Install
-------
1. Upload all files to your site root (so they live at /favicon.svg, /favicon-32.png, etc.).
2. Paste the contents of head-snippet.html into your <head>.
3. Hard-refresh (browsers aggressively cache favicons).
